name: Sun Ray
description: Brass beads and drops on gold filled French hooks. 2" long.

name: Cliff
description: From the Living On the Edge collection. Blue magnesite spears on silver, 2 1/2" long.

name: Coastal
description: Jade, turquoise, pyrite, serpentine and silver. Sterling toggle clasp. 18" with 3" pendant.

name: Liernu
description: Chalcedony, agate and gold plated beads. Gold vermeil Tree of Life charm, sterling heart charm. Set or 2 are both 7" long and strung on elastic.

name: Mermaid's Tail
description: Large natural aquamarine drop, with moss agate, green tourmaline and aquamarine briolettes on sterling silver chain. Measures 24" long and has a 3" pendant. The silver lobster clasp makes the necklace collar adjustable for different looks.

name: Moonshine
description: Spears of mother of pearl along with moonstone on 14k gold filled wire. 2" long.

name: Rosaline
description: Pink sunstone, brass, pearl, smoky quartz. Gold filled clasp. 16"L with 1.5" pendant.

name: Jaded
description: Jade, shell, mother of pearl, coral, aventurine and gold filled beads/clasp. 17" with 2.5" pendant.

name: Confection
description: Rhodocrosite pendant, agate, rose quartz and sterling silver beads and toggle clasp. 17.5"L with 2.5" drop.

name: Toasted
description:
Picture jasper, rutilated quartz, white magnesite and gold filled beads. 18.5" long and has gold filled clasp. Picture jasper center stone is naturally reversable(as shown in picture).
Also available are matching earrings, which have rutilated quartz, magnesite and smoky quartz on gold filled French hooks. 2" long.

name: Icicles
description: Faceted black onyx pendant, with layers of quartz stalactite drops and rutilated quartz on sterling silver chain. The necklace is 24" long with a 3" pendant. Sterling silver lobster clasp makes the necklace collar adjustable.

name: Black Willow
description:
Faceted labradorite piece, wrapped in sterling silver wire measures about 1.5-2"x1", strung with 2 strands of silver plated beads.
2 stranded bracelet has faceted blue labradorite and silver plated beads. Set of 2 bracelets, both have polished sterling silver Tree of Life and heart charms. 7" long, on elastic.

name: Sacred Fig
description:
Faceted amethyst, about 1.5x1", wrapped in silver wire, with 2 strands of silver plated beads.
Next is the deep purple agate, about 2x1.5", wrapped in silver wire, with 2 strands of silver plated beads.
To match either bracelet is faceted fuchsia agate with silver plated beads.
Each bracelet(sold separately or as a set) is 7", strung on elastic band with sterling silver Tree of Life charms.

name: Honey Glazed
description: Agate slice, wrapped in gold filled wire, with aceted hessonite garnet on gold filled chain. 17.5" long with 2" pendant.

name: Cardamine
description: Black lucite flowers, white mother of pearl, faceted ruby are all wrapped with white gold wire onto 14k white gold posts. Flower size is .5".

name: Nightshade
description:
Agate slice, sardonyx and white agate on gold filled chain. 18" long and the agate pendant is 3"long.
Gold filled clasp.

name: Medium Blue
description: Silver and blue agate, drusy quartz, sterling silver and Swarovski crystal beads. Sterling silver hook and eye clasp. Measures 19" long.

name: Zulu Prince
description: Jasper, pearl, brass and gold filled chain and clasp. 16"l with 3" pendant.

name: Siar
description:
Black and yellow jasper, measuring about 1.5x1", is wrapped in sterling silver wire, with faceted onyx roundelles and silver plated beads. Matching bracelet is strung with faceted yellow jade and silver plated beads.
Both have sterling Tree of Life charms and are 7" and strung on elastic.

name: Black Ice
description: 2" agate slice, faceted black onyx with 14k gold filled chain and spring ring clasp.

name: Savory
description: Garnet, chalcedony, tourmaline, smoky quartz and leather. Gold filled wire and clasp. 17" long with 2" pendant.

name: Cinnamon
description: Faceted carnelian, smoky quartz, brass and gold filled wire on gold filled French hook earring. 2" long.

name: Oasis
description: Agate, blue Opal and sterling chain and clasp. 'False' 16" inner strand. The longer strand is 20", the pendant 3" long.

name: Banyan
description:
Both bracelets are 7" long on elastic and have gold vermeil charms.
Blue agate is wrapped in 14k gold filled wire and is strung with white agate and gold plated beads.
Brown sardonyx is wrapped in 14k gold filled wire with faceted white agate and gold plated beads.

name: Hawthorn
description:
Blue Madagascar agate, wrapped in sterling silver is matched with faceted yellow jade and silver plated beads.
Matching bracelet is 2 strands of silver plated beads. Both have the sterling Tree of Life charm and are 7" on elastic band.

name: Leaflets
description:
These bracelets come in gold and silver. Each 7" bracelet has 2 strands of either gold plated or silver plated beads with the Tree of Life charm in sterling silver and gold vermeil. 
Strung on elastic for easy wear.

name: Rosabella
description: Rhodonite, quartz roundelles, black Swarovski crystals and pewter. Sterling clasp. Measures 16" and has a 2.5" extension. The Rhodonite pendant is just under 2" long.

name: Sweet Bouquet
description: Choose between magenta calla lilies with blue Amazonite, green poppy with agate or dusty blue orchid with yellow jade. Lucite flowers are all wrapped with sterling silver wire.

name: Purple Sensation
description: Amethyst, 2" purple chalcedony pendant, sterling silver chain. 17" long with silver spring ring clasp.

name: Mountain Pine
description: Quartz wrapped in silver, hematite and silver plated beads on 7" long bracelets, strung on elastic cord. Each has the sterling silver Tree of Life charm, as well as a silver heart charm, the Sara Sela exclusive.

name: Abalone Dream
description: Abalone shell, black onyx, silver and Swarovski crystal beads. 19" long with 2" abalone pendant and sterling silver toggle clasp.

name: Stalactite
description: Wood nuggets, blue magnesite slices and a raw quartz drop, wrapped in sterling silver. The necklace is 16 1/2" long with a 3" pendant. Silver spring ring clasp.

name: Eucalyptus
description:
Red coral and faceted blue amazonite are paired with faceted gold plated beads. 
Both are 7" long on elastic with the gold vermeil Tree of Life charm. Sold separately.

name: Tree Bark
description: Faceted, olive green agate, smoky quartz and moss agate are strung with gold plated beads with gold vermeil charms. 7" long on elastic band. Each bracelet is sold separately, or can be bought as a set for a great deal!

name: Rock Steady
description:
Slabs of blue magnesite, sterling silver and wood beads. 17.5" long, the longest slab of magnesite is 2.5" long. Sterling toggle clasp.
*stones lie naturally on the neck in an uneven manner, so please allow for a truly unique look.

name: Palmetto
description:
Light green chalcedony, faceted black onyx roundelles and gold plated beads. 14k gold filled wire wraps the chalcedony. Gold vermeil Tree of Life charms.
Matching bracelet has 2 strands of gold plated beads. Both bracelets are 7" on elastic to slip on the wrist.

name: White Ash
description:
These bracelets are available in quartz and hematite. Each is 7" on elastic with gold plated beads and gold vermeil Tree of Life charms.
The quartz center stone is wrapped in 14k gold filled wire with hematite.

name: Chili
description: Fire agate, sardonyx ring and faceted amber and quartz on sterling silver chain. 16" long and 3 1/2" pendant. Sterling silver clasp.

name: Cypress
description: Emerald, carnelian, copper and gold filled chain and clasp. 16.5"L with 1.5" emerald briolette.

name: Monte Cristo
description: Peach blossom jasper, agate and jade. Pink and green tourmaline, Swarovski crystal and sterling silver chain and clasp. 17" long necklace with 2" pendant.

name: Snow Drift
description: Quartz, brass and pearl. Gold filled toggle clasp and 2" brass pendant. 17" long.

name: Lime Ice
description: Sea-green agate slice, labradorite briolettes and chalcedony on sterling silver chain. The necklace is 24" long, the pendant falling on the bust line. Sterling silver lobster clasp. The pendant measures about 4" long.

name: Emmy
description: Pyrite and green emerald on gold filled wire. 2 inches long.

name: Sunset Park
description: Peach, light rose and frost flowers with either pearl, rhodonite or garnet. Lucite flowers wrapped with silver.

name: Rock It
description:
Blue Magnestite, wood and sterling silver beads and toggle clasp. 16.5" long and has a 3" extension. The longest piece of magnesite is 2.5" long.
*stones lie naturally on the neck in an uneven manner, so please allow for a truly unique look.

name: Amberly
description: Sardonyx with faceted citrine and white mother of pearl on gold filled wire. 1 1/2" long.

name: Collar Me
description: Coco tusk, wood and sardonyx beads. Sterling silver beads, chain and clasp. 18" long. The coco tusk pieces drop to 1".

name: Beachrock
description:
Blue magnesite, coconut husk and coral*. Sterling silver beads and clasp. 18" long and the center drop measures 2.5".
*all coral used by Sara Sela is coral that has died before harvesting and dyed.

name: Fringe Benefit
description: Coco tusk, blue striped agate and steel chain. Sterling silver clasp, 17" long. The agate piece is about 1"x1", the coco tusks drop to 1".

name: Flair
description: Choose between green poppies with blue amazonite or pale yellow buttercups with red aventurine. Wrapped in silver. Flowers are made of lucite.

name: Purpurea
description: Amethyst, pewter, pearl, quartz and Swarovski crystal. Silver clasp, 15"L and has a 2.5" extension. Pendant is 1.5".

name: Chinaberry
description: Cherry quartz, rock quartz, amazonite ans silver. Sterling Tree of Life charm. Strung on elastic and are 7" long. Roll on and off the wrist to wear.

name: Jonquil
description: Lucite flowers in the shade of yellow Jonquils. Faceted blue Amazonites inside. The flowers are about 1" diameter and are wrapped with silver wire to the pins.

name: Hickory
description: Black onyx and fire agate with gold plated beads. Both strung on elastic and are 7" long.

name: Dainty
description: Smoky quartz, shell, aquamarine. Gold filled chain and clasp. 17"L. 2" pendant.

name: Cerulean
description: Amazonite and brass with gold filled chain and French hooks. 2" long.

name: Blue Me
description: Agate slices, quartz and sterling silver. 16" long with a 2" drop.

name: Spruce
description: White agate and silver plated beads with drusy. Matching bracelet with blue agate and silver plated beads. Sterling wire and charm. 7".

name: Aquatic
description: Labradorite, peridot, blue topaz and Swarovski crystal. Sterling silver French hook. 1.5"L.

name: Olympia
description: Faceted Onyx, Labradorite and Swarovski crystal. Black agate pendant measures 2.5". Silver toggle clasp.

name: Sensation
description: Choose between cherry red trilliums with chrysocolla, bright yellow with turquoise or orange with amazonite. Wrapped in silver. Flowers are made of lucite.

name: Golden Flowers
description: Frosted lucite, light gold pearls, gold filled wire on hair pins. Flowers are .5" wide. Sold as a set of 2.
